            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>ciabatta pieces</strong> to a separate baking tray with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5-6 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 5,
